    "DisplayTitle": "Member Hauler Needed for Medium Shipment",
    "Description": "RED WIND LINEHAUL\n'YOUR GOODS IN GOOD HANDS'\n----------------------------   \n\nThey're doing a clean out at <EM4>~mission(Location|Address)</EM4> and have a bunch of <EM4>~mission(MissionMaxSCUSize)</EM4> or smaller waste containers that needs to be hauled out to a few different spots. (Don't ask me why. They're paying us is all I know.)\n\nDROP OFF LOCATIONS (ANY ORDER)  \n~mission(SingleToMultiToken)\n\nAnd don't forget to pack a <EM4>handheld tractor beam</EM4> to bring along.",
